<Layout>
    <div class="text-center my-2">
        <h1 class="bg-[#740B2E] text-white font-bold text-xl md:text-[50px] py-20">CASE STUDY: 
            RESTORING LIVES IN TURKIYE</h1>
      </div>



    <div class="container mx-auto  p-8 max-w-screen-2xl bg-[#aa71454D]">
        <!-- Title -->
        <div class="text-center mb-10 md:px-32">
          <p class="text-[#740B2E] font-bold text-4xl ">Restoring Lives: Azra Extends Warm Thanks to Al-Wahab Foundation for Assistance</p>
        </div>


        <div class="container px-4 md:px-20 mx-auto">
            <!-- Main Container -->
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
              <!-- Image Section -->
              <div class="md:w-1/3 my-auto md:mx-8 flex-shrink-0">
                <img
                  src="https://alwahabfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/IMG_1245-1-768x576.jpg"
                  alt="Water Crisis Image"
                  class="w-96 h-96 object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <!-- Text Section -->
              <div class=" pt-4 md:pt-0  md:w-2/3">
               
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-grey text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-justify"
                >
                Azra Extends Warm Thanks to Al-Wahab Foundation for Assistance

                Meet Azra – a resilient individual living in the city of Hatay, Turkiye. Like many others in her community, Azra found herself facing unprecedented challenges due to miserable conditions after the earthquake. Hatay was struck by a series of natural disasters, leaving its residents in a state of emergency, struggling to access basic necessities for survival.
                </p>
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-grey text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-justify"
                >
                The region experienced severe disruptions to its infrastructure and services, leaving families like Azra’s dealing with food scarcity, lack of shelter, and limited access to essential items. With the sudden loss of livelihood opportunities and resources, the community was in dire need of urgent assistance.
                </p>
                <p
                class="mt-2 text-grey text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-justify "
              >
              Azra, a mother of four, shared the hardships they faced daily:
              </p>
           
               
              </div>
            
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 md:px-20 mx-auto" >
            <p
            class="mt-2 text-grey text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-justify "
          >
          “My name is Azra, and I reside in Hatay with my family. Our lives were turned upside down by the unusual conditions that struck our city. We lost our home, our belongings, and our means of income. Providing for my children became an overwhelming challenge, as we struggled to find food, clean water, and other necessities. It was a time of immense uncertainty and fear for our future.”
          </p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-grey text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-justify">Recognizing the dire situation faced by Azra’s family and others in the region, Al-Wahab Foundation swiftly intervened to provide an Emergency Relief Package. This comprehensive package included essential food items and other necessities sufficient to serve Azra’s family and others for better survival during these trying times.</p>
      
          
            <p class="mt-2 text-grey text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-justify ">Through the generosity of compassionate donors, Al-Wahab Foundation’s Emergency Relief Package brought a glimmer of hope to Azra’s family. The relief provisions offered them a lifeline, enabling them to cope with the challenges and rebuild their lives amidst the crisis.</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-grey text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-justify ">Azra expressed her heartfelt gratitude to Al-Wahab Foundation:</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-grey text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-justify ">“We are deeply grateful to the Al-Wahab Foundation and Mufti Abdul Wahab for their understanding and support during this difficult time. The Emergency Relief Package they provided has been a true blessing for my family. It gave us access to essential food, clean water, and hygiene supplies that were hard to come by after the disaster. I am thankful to Almighty Allah that we still have got kind people like Mufti Abdul Wahab and the dedicated team of Al-Wahab Foundation to help suffering families in bringing ease to them.”</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-grey text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-justify ">Through its Emergency Relief Project, Al-Wahab Foundation has made a significant impact in Hatay, Turkiye, providing vital assistance to families like Azra’s, who are facing unforeseen challenges. The relief provisions not only addressed immediate needs but also offered a glimmer of hope and a sense of security in the midst of uncertainty.</p>
         
            <p class="mt-2 text-grey text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-justify ">Join hands with Al-Wahab Foundation and extend your support to our brothers and sisters in Turkiye by donating at <a class="font-bold text-maroon hover:text-customBeige" href="">www.alwahabfoundation.org  </a> or call us at <a class="font-bold text-maroon hover:text-customBeige">020 8903 8944.</a></p>
       
           
          </div>

          <div class="flex justify-center mt-10 sm:mt-12">
            <a
              href="#"
              class="bg-maroon hover:bg-customBeige text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 sm:px-8 rounded-full uppercase text-sm sm:text-base"
            >
             KNOW MORE 
            </a>
          </div>

      </div>


</Layout>